        "title": "Greater Austin's bike retail map",
        "subtitle": "A tour of independents, chains, and e-bike specialists",
        "body": "<p>This dataset profiles 12 bicycle and e-bike shops from central Austin up through Round Rock, Cedar Park, and Pflugerville. Five are plotted on the map; the rest live in the full report while we geocode their storefronts.</p>",
